[MESSAGE]Let's talk about apprenticeships and how you can offer them to your chefs. 

By offering apprenticeships, your apprentices can gradually learn from Armand's recipe skill and wisdom and eventually become as skillful as him.

Let's take a look at this by opening the _Staff Panel_.
[POSITION]475,32
[DIMENSION]310,250
[HINT]

[MESSAGE]Under the _Staff Panel_, you can pick the chef that you wish to select as your apprentice. Go ahead and try to offer an apprenticeship to "%s %s".
[POSITION]475,32
[DIMENSION]310,250
[HINT]

[MESSAGE]Armand can offer a maximum of three chefs to become his apprentice. If you already have three and would like to offer another chef the opportunity, you may terminate a relationship with one of your current apprentices and then offer the empty slot to the new chef.

_Left-click_ on the _Next_ button to continue.
[POSITION]475,32
[DIMENSION]310,250
[HINT]

[MESSAGE]Excellent! Now that you have learned how to take chefs under your wing, you may go ahead and play with it some more. Who knows? A future star chef may be in one of them!
